{"tid":398801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢施龍爪手　捏31歲打機女胸","createTime":"2017-09-13T12:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T13:19:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06aacbf7d8aba7d3c271003ced745bbaa7e8b7f9","tid":398801,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>南亞漢施龍爪手　捏31歲打機女胸</strong>　　<br />\n<br />\n南亞淫狼色膽包天，公然「胸襲」打機女。現場為深水埗北河街一間遊戲機中心，今午2時許，一名31歲女子獨自在上址打機消遣，期間，一名南亞漢悄然趨近坐到其旁邊，並佯裝打機，但不斷偷瞄女事主。由於事主玩得樂極忘形，沒有留意已成「南亞狼」的獵物。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，該名南亞漢窺準事主毫無戒心時，突然從身旁向她施以「龍爪手」胸襲，女事主嚇得失聲不知所措，驚魂甫定才大嗌：「非禮！」惟南亞淫狼已奪門逃去。遊戲機中心職員獲知發生非禮，隨即協助及報警求助。警方接報到場，曾在現場附近兜截，惟並無發現，案件列作非禮，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"3b0043db7cfd105f692a377686c20818ff44da65","tid":398801,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"可惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa9a7eb0b6cac67ffc3ee7c3d181977f1f4f56c","tid":398801,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"31歲仲打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c64f93e1732c2888f711144745a844eeb0e4605","tid":398801,"uid":11844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>31歲仲打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定係個啲千炮捕魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6c1a542b48d0a456cbb4a7623d9e40766af9be","tid":398801,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:19:04.000Z","msg":"一定好大波"}]}